text: konege avanu mosadinda avarannu olisikondanu mattu avaribbaru a marada phalavannu savidaga avara guptangagalu avara (parasparara) munde prakatavagi bittavu mattu avaribbaru svargada elegalinda tam'mannu muccikolla todagidaru. (Aga) avara odeyanu avarannu karedu helidanu; nanu nim'mannu a maradinda tadediralillave? Athava saitananu nim'mibbara paligu spasta satruvagiddanendu nanu nimage heliralillave
